column1: IF ccr_thf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_pt_one_d is MF 1 AND ccr_sa_thb_d is MF 1 AND ccr_ths_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
IF ccr_dha_d is MF 1 AND ccr_thdoc_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_cortisone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_zoa_dhe_d is MF 2 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_tha_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
